How to setup Android SDK for Visual Studio Android Emulator step by step

Download and install Visual Studio Android Emulator at https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/vs/msft-android-emulator/

vs_emulatorsetup.exe

Run Visual Studio Android Emulator needs to turn on Hyper-V netwrok adapter

You do not have permission to modify internal Hyper-V Netwrok adapter settings, which are required to run the emulator

got to Hyper-V manager and remove service in Hyper-V

 
************************


go to cmd
type adb devices

C:\Users\dell>adb devices
'adb' is not recognized as an internal or external command,
operable program or batch file.

need add android sdk path to regedit

Computer\HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\WOW6432Node\WOW6432Node right click to create new key "Android SDK Tools", right click "Android SDK Tools" add new Key Name = "Path"
"Value Data" = D:\WorkerArea\DasCom\DasCom_MobilePrinter\SDK\SDK\Android\Dascom SDK 2021.03.23 6720

start Emulater


